    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated restoration project or a source for parts. The body shows significant signs of age, including advanced rust on the lower panels and several noticeable dents. Mechanically, the car requires substantial work as the engine currently struggles to stay running and the transmission exhibits slipping. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. Please expect to tow this vehicle upon purchase.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable driving experience for its next owner. The exterior is clean and presents well, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and small surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is tidy and the upholstery is free of tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly, the transmission shifts as it should, and all major electronics are fully functional. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that has many miles left to give.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic ride! This well-maintained vehicle is in good condition and ready for its next adventure. It offers a smooth, reliable driving experience with a clean interior and a solid exterior that shows it's been cared for. It\u2019s a wonderful choice for anyone looking for a dependable car that still has plenty of great miles to go!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
